profile:
PELLA Construction is a residential and commercial contractor proudly serving the Kitchener and surrounding area for over 10 years. 

PELLA Construction specializes in new home construction, additions, renovations, finished basements, detached garages, decks, window and door replacements, siding and aluminum work as well as roofing. We have finished many multi-residential properties in terms of hardwood and laminate flooring installations, doors and trim and kitchens. 

With our high attention to detail, professional business relationships with other licensed trades and suppliers, quality, craftsmanship, honesty and integrity we are able to guarantee our work and your satisfaction completed within a reasonable and timely fashion.

Feel free to contact us to arrange a free, no obligation estimate regarding any and all of your construction and remodeling needs.
